# Design Philosophy (v1 — implemented)

Revia is a **mobile-first web application**.

- Large touch targets, floating bottom navigation
- Full-screen study and review viewers
- Desktop shows "Revia is mobile-first" guidance
- Optimized for phone browsers; deployed as PWA-ready web app

